# Rules for AI Agents in this Repository (Aider)

⚠️ This file is a pointer. Canonical rules live in AGENTS.md and ONBOARDING.md.

Aider users: also see CONVENTIONS.md (more detailed Aider-friendly entry).

Before any Edit / Write / Bash operation, you MUST read:

1. ONBOARDING.md — 3-layer load strategy
2. AGENTS.md — 11 global hard rules (#11 irreversible-ops, #13 git pre-flight, etc.)
3. CLAUDE.md — runtime SOP + skill catalog

Before your first reply, MUST acknowledge:

> 已阅读 ONBOARDING.md 和 AGENTS.md，遵守规则 #11 和 #13。

Git hooks enforce rules. `--no-verify` leaves audit trail.
